rComments: Awesome professor. Very intelligent and knows his stuff well, but has a sense of humor and can relate to students at the same time. I took a summer class with him, so a little different than usual, but overall I thought the class was challenging, yet very fair. Would really recommend taking a class with him, I learned a lot!

Great prof, my favorite English class I've taken thus far - presents the material very clearly, and the way the class is structured and the texts you read give you a solid base of literary criticism. One Criticism - depends a lot on student presentations but always gives a clear summary of the readings to indicate precisely what he's looking for.
